Customer Portal and App 
o Customer can create a login using their policy details 
o Customer should be able to change the correspondence address 
o Customer should be able to change the billing cycle 
o Customer should be able to make electronic payment. 
o Customer should be able to submit claims. 
o Customer should be able to submit any supporting document 
o Customer should be notified and alerted if any status change 
happens on claims. 
o Customer should be able to check the Partner Service providers 
(Repair workshop, authorized service station, Car Rental) based on 
this location or zip address. 
o Customer should be able to keep track of repair based on work 
order and progress report submitted by the Repair agency. 